title: László Deutsch
text: László Deutsch (born 9 March 1999) is a <a href="Hungary">Hungarian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who plays for <a href="Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20I">OTP Bank Liga</a> club <a href="Pusk%C3%A1s%20Akad%C3%A9mia%20FC">Puskás Akadémia FC</a>.
